        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Save Our Afghan Allies Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense to report to Congress a plan for admitting and relocating to the United States citizens of Afghanistan under an existing program. (The program provides special immigrant visas to eligible individuals who worked for U.S. or NATO forces in Afghanistan on or after October 7, 2001.)</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
